466
00:19:39,913 --> 00:19:42,380
Man #4: Yeah.
I heard someone say

467
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:44,850
the toughest ones
are secretly plotting something.

468
00:19:44,918 --> 00:19:46,852
Monster: No, no. Not that rumor.

469
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,854
It's about
a more dangerous monster.

470
00:19:48,922 --> 00:19:50,589
Monster #2: What do ya mean?

471
00:19:50,591 --> 00:19:52,524
Monster #3: You didn't hear?

472
00:19:52,593 --> 00:19:54,593
I'm told the place
has now become terrifying

473
00:19:54,661 --> 00:19:56,362
for both humans and monsters.

