00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:38,236
Saitama: Ah. 'Kay, thanks.

478
00:20:38,305 --> 00:20:42,307
Genos: Also, your rank has
gone from last place, 388th,

479
00:20:42,376 --> 00:20:44,777
to 342nd. Congratulations.

480
00:20:44,779 --> 00:20:46,311
Saitama: Oh? Wait.

481
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:47,846
'Cause of that panic guy?

482
00:20:47,914 --> 00:20:50,448
Guess he boosted my ranking.
Cool.

483
00:20:50,518 --> 00:20:53,384
So I think it's been
about a week now.

484
00:20:53,454 --> 00:20:54,586
Have you done anything?

