00:20:54,655 --> 00:20:56,321
Genos: No. Not yet, anyway.

486
00:20:56,390 --> 00:20:58,390
Saitama: Well,
you've still got time, I guess.

487
00:20:58,392 --> 00:21:00,859
Genos: I am still ranked last
in class s for ability,

488
00:21:00,928 --> 00:21:02,527
17th place.

489
00:21:02,596 --> 00:21:06,998
Saitama: Heh. Sounds like
you still need lots of training.

490
00:21:07,067 --> 00:21:08,867
Genos: But according
to popularity rankings

491
00:21:08,936 --> 00:21:12,470
voted on by the public,
