492
00:21:12,540 --> 00:21:13,939
Saitama: Why?!

493
00:21:14,007 --> 00:21:17,476
Genos: "A 19-year old genius
who made his debut in class s."

494
00:21:17,478 --> 00:21:18,410
"He is fantastic."

495
00:21:18,478 --> 00:21:19,878
"He is so handsome."

496
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:22,548
"Love how he refuses to do
media interviews. Cool."

497
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:24,616
- Those kinds of comments.
- Saitama: Good god.

498
00:21:24,685 --> 00:21:27,486
How are you not embarrassed
to read those out loud?

499
00:21:27,554 --> 00:21:28,753
Genos: Quite simple.

500
00:21:28,823 --> 00:21:30,889
This is based on impressions
from my photo.

501
00:21:30,958 --> 00:21:32,758
They are not
true evaluations of me.

502
00:21:32,826 --> 00:21:33,959
I think nothing of them.

503
00:21:34,027 --> 00:21:35,627
Saitama: Oh? Yeah?

504
00:21:35,629 --> 00:21:37,362
Genos: "The cyborg prince."

505
00:21:37,431 --> 00:21:40,632
"Behind the steely exterior,
I feel his fragile self."

506
00:21:40,701 --> 00:21:42,434
"Top five handsomest heroes."

507
00:21:42,502 --> 00:21:43,969
Saitama: Enough already!

